headline: Why The Narrative Around Oracle Is Shifting After Cloud and AI Developments
summary: Oracle's latest analyst consensus price target has edged down, moving from $344.04 to $342.28. This cautious revision comes amid evolving views on the company’s prospects, shaped by both bullish and bearish developments in its cloud momentum and AI strategy. Stay tuned to discover how you can keep up with these shifting perspectives and future updates to Oracle’s investment narrative.
